data.description: Experience living at its finest in this custom built contemporary home featuring 22' ceilings, unobstructed golf course views and a dozen skylights to let the Florida sunshine stream in.  Located on a half acre elevated lot in the premier golf course community of River Wilderness in Parrish, this three bedroom, three bath pool home boasts a modern design that is both stylish and functional. As you enter, you will be greeted by a spacious open floor plan with graduating levels culminating with a dramatic lanai overlooking the 8th fairway.  Enjoy all four seasons  relaxing by the pool, soak your cares away in the Hot Spring spa, grill a special meal in the outdoor kitchen and then head inside to enjoy a beverage in front of the gas fireplace. Offering a spacious office/den with shelving and built ins for easy work from home accommodations.  The left side of the home encompasses the owner's suite, featuring a large bedroom and sitting area, two walk in closets, a luxurious and updated bath and a private entrance to the screened porch and lanai.  Two guest rooms with a shared bath on the opposite side grant privacy for all.  Pride in ownership is apparent as this property has been lovingly upgraded and maintained; new roof in 2022, extended paver circular driveway, new GE Monogram refrigerator and dishwasher, replacement of all skylights, Ecosmart tankless water heater, all bath's remodeled, Pebble Tec pool resurface, new Hot Spring spa, Powerworx Whole Home Energy System and Plantation shutters throughout.  The oversized climate controlled 3 car garage with Hurricane garage doors, new attic pulldown ladder system offers a work room, built in storage, separate space ideal for a wine cellar and ample closets for storage. No CDD fees and optional membership in The Club at River Wilderness make this a perfect choice for the discriminating Buyer.  This property offers an assumable VA Loan for qualified Buyers.
